---
import PageLayout from '../../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';

const relatedLogs = (await getCollection('en/log', ({ data }) =>
  data.published !== false && data.project_tag === 'AutoTrading'
)).sort((a, b) => b.data.date.getTime() - a.data.date.getTime());

const relatedInsights = (await getCollection('en/insight', ({ data }) =>
  data.published !== false && data.project_tag === 'AutoTrading'
)).sort((a, b) => b.data.date.getTime() - a.data.date.getTime());
---

<PageLayout title="AI Auto-Trading Experiment" description="An experiment building and running an automated trading system with AI and ₩5M. No code written by hand — just rules, an AI assistant, and real capital on the line.">
  <div class="project-detail">
    <a href="/en/projects" class="back-link">← Projects</a>

    <div class="project-header">
      <span class="project-status status-active">🟢 Live</span>
      <h1>AI Auto-Trading Experiment</h1>
      <p class="project-meta">Current version: <strong>v1.4</strong> · Last updated: <strong>2026-04-24</strong></p>
    </div>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>An experiment building and running an automated trading system with AI and ₩5M.<br>
      A non-coder handles judgment; AI handles execution. That collaboration structure is the core.</p>
      <p>The goal isn't profit.<br>
      The goal is the experience of building a system where AI operates real capital — by hand.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Current Status</h2>
      <p>🟢 <strong>Live Account Active</strong> — 5 bugs fixed, 6 strategy changes (2026-04-24). Wrong cash field corrected (switched to ord_psbl_cash_amt), 18 duplicate KT sell reservations removed. Regime detection redesigned to 5-condition scoring + 2-day confirmation. Cash reserve ratios tied to total assets (bull 20% / neutral 35% / bear 60%). Closing balance ₩4,890,000. (As of 2026-04-24)</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Collaboration Structure</h2>
      <table class="update-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Role</th><th>Owner</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Strategy direction + judgment</td><td>메타철부지 (GPT)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Code analysis + execution</td><td>Claude Code</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Direction setting + final call</td><td>Operator (철부지)</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Current Strategy</h2>
      <table class="update-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Setting</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Buy signal</td><td>RSI(Wilder) 40–65</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Trend filter</td><td>MA20 deviation — large-cap ≤ 14% / standard ≤ 7% (with sell buffer)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Position size</td><td>20% per stock / max ₩1,000,000 · max 5 stocks</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Max capital</td><td>₩5,000,000 (50% of cash balance)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Cash reserve</td><td>Bull 20% / Neutral 35% / Bear 60% (tied to total assets)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Regime detection</td><td>5-condition scoring · 2 consecutive days same signal → regime change</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Buy scans</td><td>3×/day (10:00 / 13:00 / 14:00)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Take profit</td><td>+6% fixed or trailing stop</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Trailing stop</td><td>Activated at +4% / sell at –2% from peak</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Stop loss</td><td>–3%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Stock universe</td><td>20 tickers (sector-diversified)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Same-day re-entry</td><td>Blocked</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Update History</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>2026-04-24 · v1.4</strong> — 5 bugs fixed, 6 strategy changes. Wrong cash field (prvs_rcdl_excc_amt → ord_psbl_cash_amt) corrected — orders restored. 18 duplicate KT PENDING_SELL reservations removed + deduplication logic added. MA20 deviation threshold split by stock type (large-cap 14% / standard 7%), buy-sell buffer zone added. Regime detection switched from single KOSPI close to 5-condition scoring with 2-day confirmation; cash reserve ratios (bull 20% / neutral 35% / bear 60%) tied to total assets. Realized P&amp;L –₩93,000 (Kia · KT stop-losses). 4 orders executed. Closing balance ₩4,890,000.</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-22</strong> — Live day 3. 2 stop-losses executed (KB Financial &amp; Kakao, –₩61,800 total). MA60 filter correctly blocked 3 downtrend stocks (NAVER, Kia, Hyundai Motor) — first live validation of 4/21 API replacement (65 data points, MA20+MA60 normal). Budget safety margin (safe_budget×0.95) partial validation: success at 13:00, failed again at 14:00. KT entered as new position. Closing balance ₩4,906,290.</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-21</strong> — MA60 API replacement complete. Switched from inquire-daily-price (fixed 30 candles) to inquire-daily-itemchartprice (65 candles). Validated in live trading on 4/22 — downtrend filter working correctly.</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-20</strong> — Live account day 1. 2 bugs fixed (stale paper-trading token in cache / MA60=None fallback to MA20). First 5 buys executed (Kakao, Kia, KB Financial, Shinhan, NAVER), ₩4,690,300 deployed, ₩305,970 cash remaining. End-of-day unrealized P&amp;L: –₩54,030 (–1.08%), all positions held. Telegram daily summary and data export confirmed.</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-17 · v1.3</strong> — 1-week paper trade complete, live account switch confirmed. 4 bugs fixed (buy amount as loss / loss limit hard-coded / cash balance stuck / account number format). Kakao trailing stop triggered (+3.01%, +₩30,060). Weekly realized P&amp;L: +₩45,060 (+0.58%). Live account API connection verified.</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-16</strong> — STEP 11·12 complete. Buy scans reduced 4→3/day. Stock universe expanded 5→20. Deviation cap loosened 5%→7%. Max holdings raised 3→5 stocks.</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-15</strong> — STEP 10 complete. Auto-recovery for stale lock files (psutil PID validation). Trailing stop fired in live trading. Samsung Electronics +3.57% auto-sold. Realized P&amp;L: +₩15,000.</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-14</strong> — Switched to live trading. Trailing stop refinement, balance fallback logic, post-market Telegram summary. First real order executed (Kakao 20 shares @ ₩48,350)</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-10</strong> — Production-grade stabilization. Balance field fix / API retry / duplicate buy &amp; process prevention / hold_days fix / IS_PAPER safeguard</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-09</strong> — Python module cache issue identified and buy cycle restored. Scheduler restart SOP created</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-08 · v1.1</strong> — Dual market regime filter / volume filter / sell condition branching / same-day re-entry block / log structure overhaul</li>
        <li><strong>2026-04-07 · v1.0</strong> — KIS API integration, rule engine, Telegram alerts, scheduler MVP complete</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Roadmap</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Monday pre-market 08:50 — BULL signal recorded? (first live validation of 5-condition regime scoring)</li>
        <li>Monday 10:00 scan — Samsung Electronics passes updated deviation threshold and buy executes?</li>
        <li>Compile per-ticker win rate statistics (in 2 weeks)</li>
        <li>Review adding a volume spike condition</li>
        <li>Establish monthly ticker rebalancing criteria</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Related Logs</h2>
      {relatedLogs.length > 0 ? (
        <ul class="related-list">
          {relatedLogs.map(post => (
            <li>
              <a href={`/en/log/${post.slug}`}>{post.data.title}</a>
              <span class="post-date">{post.data.date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric' })}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      ) : (
        <p class="placeholder">No related logs yet.</p>
      )}
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Related Insights</h2>
      {relatedInsights.length > 0 ? (
        <ul class="related-list">
          {relatedInsights.map(post => (
            <li>
              <a href={`/en/insight/${post.slug}`}>{post.data.title}</a>
              <span class="post-date">{post.data.date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric' })}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      ) : (
        <p class="placeholder">No related insights yet. Add <code>project_tag: "AutoTrading"</code> to any insight file to link it here automatically.</p>
      )}
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .project-detail {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    color: #1976d2;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .project-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .project-header h1 {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .project-status {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .status-experimental {
    background-color: #fce4ec;
    color: #c62828;
  }

  .status-active {
    background-color: #e8f5e9;
    color: #2e7d32;
  }

  .project-meta {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section p {
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .placeholder {
    color: #999;
  }

  .section ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .section ul a {
    color: #1976d2;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .section ul a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .related-list {
    padding-left: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .related-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .related-list a {
    color: #1976d2;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .related-list a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .post-date {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #888;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .section h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  .update-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #444;
  }

  .update-table th {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .update-table td {
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .update-table tr:nth-child(even) td {
    background-color: #fafafa;
  }
</style>
